Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:15.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}独自一人叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:19.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大家又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:23.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}总觉得很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:29.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}广阔的大地上 一粒种子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:32.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸展开根系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:40.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}又结出青色的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:45.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要早些成为橙色的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:48.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沐浴着你的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:52.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}理想和梦想不断膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:55.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快察觉到吧 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:22:58.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天也品尝了橙子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:02.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}依然酸涩 不禁落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:05.82,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不能让它像我一样被丢弃
